import hashlib
import urllib.parse

def generate_token(seed):
    hashed_seed = hashlib.sha3_256(seed.encode()).hexdigest()
    token = hashed_seed[:129]
    encoded_token = urllib.parse.quote(token)
    return encoded_token

import hashlib
import urllib.parse

def generate_token(seed):
